    "The system also employs synthetic datasets, created to mimic complex, ambiguous, or highly context-specific queries, thereby providing a comprehensive assessment of the model's retrieval prowess across a spectrum of challenging scenarios.",
    "ResultsThis section lists the outcomes derived from the experimental evaluation of the reinforcement learning-enhanced LLaMA model, herein referred to as Optimized LLaMA, against the standard LLaMA model, referred to as Baseline LLaMA.",
